      "content": "but if a \"way to make the pain more bearable\" is just an illusion, what's the point of even trying to make it bearable? if everything is just a temporary distraction from nothingness, isn't there a certain kind of peace in just... not participating anymore? like, if the universe doesn't care, why should I have to keep struggling against it?",
